name: MongBNB
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
MONGBNB is the meme coin
the community always deserved
The MongBsc coin was born to match the goals of the of the original Mong on ETH, BSC community aligned with Mong Culture will help to grow Mong community and achieve all the goals. Friendship, degenerate meme culture and good vibes.
We believe every good meme coin deserves a dope PFP. Mongs NFT have supported the MongMob since its inception so we decided to allocate 6.9% of the token supply to Mongs NFT holders. These tokens will be unlocked as we reach the following milestones.
